freedays.app
Class FreeDayR

java.lang.Object
  freedays.app.FreeDay
      freedays.app.FreeDaysRCMatch
          freedays.app.FreeDayR

public class FreeDayR
extends FreeDaysRCMatch

Class that represents a TypeR free day request. Such a request can be made:

  • on demand if the user worked an extra day (in weekend)
  • in conjunction with a TypeC waiting request

Author:
fmacicasan
